 |   C                     ELSE
 |   C                     MOVELLTR6      K#INVN    P
 |   C                     ENDIF
 |    *
 |   C           #PL19F    SETLLAB#PL19F
 |   C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN95
 |   C           *IN95     DOWEQ*OFF
 |   C           #PL19F    READEAB#PL19F                 95
 |   C           *IN95     IFEQ *OFF
 |   C           BASKJY    ANDEQ*BLANK
